    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS for optimized volumetric efficiency. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct mechanical linkage to the rear-mounted M Variable Differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. While the aesthetics show honest wear consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, delivering sharp throttle response and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. An ideal candidate for the purist seeking a mechanically sound chassis with documented maintenance of critical failure points.",
