    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a well-cared-for luxury SUV that presents beautifully and drives even better. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though a thorough walk-around reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, three-inch scuff on the passenger-side rear bumper from a tight parking maneuver. The alloy wheels are clean, with only very light curb rash on the front right rim. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is firm and intact, showing only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car has been maintained with an open checkbook. It features a complete service history, with the most recent oil service and multi-point inspection completed just 500 miles ago. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires are matching all-seasons with approximately 65% tread life remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car depreciation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
