    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically sound, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014essential preventative measures for this chassis. The naturally aspirated powerplant pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from synchronized individual throttle bodies and a fresh valve adjustment. Handling is precise, aided by a factory limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression and linear power delivery. A mechanically honest M-car for the purist.",
